   "question": "Where does Fury Warrior Phase 1 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 301 top-ranked Fury Warrior DPS parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 1 (Karazhan, Gruul's Lair and Magtheridon), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
